_header: A wonder meet that God hath hight
_description: Verses in the sermon, Panem nostrum cotidianum da nobis hodie — one couplet

CULIi38.Transcription:
A wonder mete þat god hat hetthHitȝ haȝt newe name
                    wyde kyd
